    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already changed my passwords and used 2fa. nothing changed. the posts are still happening. it's not just random spam, it's like... it's using my specific slang and even talking about things i mentioned in private messages months ago. it feels less like a hack and more like the accounts aren't even mine anymore. like the \"me\" on those apps is a separate entity that just keeps going without me. does that even make sense? it's like i died online and something else took my place.",
